import './Navigation.css'
import { Navbar, Container, Nav, NavDropdown } from 'react-bootstrap'
import { NavLink } from 'react-router-dom'
import { useContext } from 'react'
import { AuthContext } from '../../context/auth.context'

const Navigation = () => {
    console.log('el user --->', AuthContext)


    const { user, logOutUser, isLoggedIn } = useContext(AuthContext)

    console.log('el user --->', user)

    return (
        <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="dark" variant="dark" >

            <Navbar.Brand href="#home">gelioX</Navbar.Brand>
            <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
            <Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
                {/* <Nav className="me-auto">
                </Nav> */}
                <Nav>
                    <NavLink to="/" className="nav-link">Inicio</NavLink>
                    <NavLink to="/productos" className="nav-link">Productos</NavLink>
                    <NavDropdown title="Dropdown" id="collasible-nav-dropdown" >
                        {
                            isLoggedIn
                                ?
                                user && <>
                                    <NavDropdown.Item><NavLink to="/perfil" className="nav-link justify-content-end text-dark">Hola, {user.username}</NavLink></NavDropdown.Item>
                                    <NavDropdown.Item><NavLink to="/perfil" className="nav-link justify-content-end text-dark">Ver perfil</NavLink></NavDropdown.Item>
                                    <NavDropdown.Divider />
                                    <NavDropdown.Item onClick={logOutUser}>Cerrar sesión</NavDropdown.Item>

                                </>



                                :
                                <>
                                    <NavDropdown.Item><NavLink to="/registro" className="nav-link text-dark">Registro</NavLink></NavDropdown.Item>
                                    <NavDropdown.Item><NavLink to="/inicio-sesion" className="nav-link text-dark">Iniciar sesión</NavLink></NavDropdown.Item>

                                </>

                        }
                    </NavDropdown>
                </Nav>
            </Navbar.Collapse>

        </Navbar >
    )
}

export default Navigation
